title: [Enemy Ship, Main Deck]
description: A bronze bell rings out the half-hour of the watch beneath the sail fastened to mast towering overhead.  Down a steep companionway, a pair of crewmen roll barrels into the cargo hold, while a cabin boy emerges from below juggling an armload of cannonballs to replenish the munitions alongside some cannons on deck.  A section of rigging has snapped loose above some debris, the rope whipping back and forth in the constant breeze.
paths: Obvious paths: east, west, up, down
